release_note: Introducing: LUMINA a beautiful new film effect. Add a dreamy glowy halo around all the pockets of light in your videos and photos. LUMINA was built with halation a magical phenomenon that is typically only found in film but can now be experienced in this magical little app. LUMINA looks great on all types of content but we think you ll especially love it on videos. We can t wait to see the art that you create. xx Team Tezza

Soft moody tones. A perfect sugar dusting of grain. Meet SUEDE your new editing obsession. We say it every time but this truly might be the new number one. It s impossible to make a photo look bad with this thing. Suede isn t the only thing in this update! We also have bug fixes and pre trim when importing clips. We have so much coming in the next few months so buckle up folks. xx Team Tezza

Drumroll please..... the moment you ve all been waiting for.... STUDIO is live! Well over a year in the making this is our beautiful new video editor. Not only is it powerful and easy to use but it has all of the special Tezza sauce on top: curated presets film shop effects killer fonts awesome music and so much more. We are nothing without our incredible community of artists and creators and we hope you enjoy using Studio as much as we ve enjoyed building it for you. And this is just the beginning! We ll be adding so much more to this thing as time goes on and will continue to make it amazing with your feedback and support. We can t wait to see the art that you create Studio. xx Team Tezza

NEW FILM SHOP EFFECT: LOFI An edgy screen grain with a pop of old school digital camera goodness welcome LOFI our latest entry to the Film Shop. And we weren t done there. Silk fixes Vinyl fixes bulk saving fixes you name it we fixed it. We hope you love the new lofi effect as much as we do! Truly one of our faves.
